CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 8, 1964, pg. 1, reads: "United Nations Group - Withe their teacher, Mrs. Norwilda Marshall (standing extreme right), one part of the sixth grade United Nation Recitation Group is shown posing for The Courier photographer. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of boys and girls of the sixth grade United Nations Recitation Group, posed with teacher Norwilda Marshall on stage at Miller Elementary School
